@startuml
title CSI/RSSI Experiment Program - System Context

left to right direction
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

actor "Research Operator" as Operator
actor "Subject (Human)" as Subject

rectangle "Laptop A (TX)" as LaptopTX {
  [run_tx_laptop.sh]
}

rectangle "Laptop B (RX)" as LaptopRX {
  [tools/exp]
  [csi_capture.cli]
  [csi_capture.experiment]
}

node "ESP32 TX Board\n(target_profile=esp32s3_csi_v1)" as TXBoard
node "ESP32 RX Board\n(target_profile=esp32s3_csi_v1)" as RXBoard
database "Dataset Storage\n(experiments/ + data/experiments/)" as DatasetStore
folder "Reports and Analytics\n(out/ + artifacts/)" as Reports

Operator --> LaptopTX : flash/start TX firmware
Operator --> LaptopRX : run capture/train/eval commands
Subject --> RXBoard : static sign / movement scenario
LaptopTX --> TXBoard : idf.py build/flash\ncsi_send
LaptopRX --> RXBoard : idf.py build/flash\ncsi_recv + serial read
TXBoard --> RXBoard : Wi-Fi traffic + CSI
LaptopRX --> DatasetStore : write manifests\nwrite capture files
LaptopRX --> Reports : train models\ngenerate metrics

@enduml
